query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(s t1) */ select count(*)
from site AS s
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name = 'stackoverflow' AND t1.name IN ('amazon-web-services',
'android-activity',
'dependencies',
'ide',
'ios6',
'keras',
'laravel-4',
'memory-leaks',
'nginx',
'reflection',
'silverlight',
'sql',
'uiview',
'windows-7')
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 5 AND q1.favorite_count <= 5000
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id AND acc.website_url ilike '%io'
inner join badge AS b1
on s.site_id = b1.site_id AND b1.user_id = u1.id;
